哋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd2eb7e6aa6891266da43f9f7644a9d69da161f9","tid":2350964,"uid":379491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T20:10:19.000Z","msg":"對住家母乜撚都要講多謝唔該<br />\n唔係佢就系撚住塊面成日話乜你甘無禮貌<br />\n奉旨我嚟幫你呀唔該多謝都冇聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bda12d82d3f5bbb1e3a99bd9ce6a6d82c906c10c","tid":2350964,"uid":360601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T20:18:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3c4e455368a347dc193ebcfc23fb40563e159484","tid":2350964,"uid":223912,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T21:10:21.000Z","msg":"老豆無啦啦比錢我嘅時候<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e3c534b86eee024b7a6e9586b7de9ac2cbb2949","tid":2350964,"uid":141097,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T00:01:41.000Z","msg":"我都想講不過好似好難講出口<br />\n難為情"},{"pid":"e5381eaec63359c216f16c0471723f7acb8949e6","tid":2350964,"uid":356078,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T01:58:46.000Z","msg":"佢地生我出世, 要我受左咁多苦<br />\n我一句都怨過佢地<br />\n仲要賺錢俾佢地駛<br />\n係未應該佢地同我講多謝"},{"pid":"8d97f13dae51528a7a2e888d44db9a8f13023363","tid":2350964,"uid":386926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T02:22:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa1a5b460bbfb6d0e5bc795aa2932c1042dac12d","tid":2350964,"uid":9901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5cc672023ab260c07aebb9ae4b869ed8576c39f9","tid":2350964,"uid":387407,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T19:57:23.000Z","msg":"由細到大同父母感情好好，成日都會真情對話，唔會怕羞講I love you或者多謝。<br />\n<br />\n多謝爹哋媽咪，我愛你地！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T02:40:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/nor